   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "> Section </uicontrol> button to show detailed information about the
         measurement data of a section. You can quickly change to another section by pressing the
         Section arrow buttons.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Press on a bottle image to show only that bottle and related information. Press again on
         the bottle image to show all bottles again. Press on a bottle to see more data about a
         specific cavity.<fig id="fig_rxp_5rn_fcc" class="- topic/fig ">
            <image href="media/image1.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_sxp_5rn_fcc"
                   align="center"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Press on a graph to zoom on the image. Press again on the graph to return to the normal
            view.<fig id="fig_hxn_1sn_fcc" class="- topic/fig ">
            <image href="media/image2.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   align="center"
                   id="image_ixn_1sn_fcc"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Press on the up and down arrow keys to change the Region. Press on the<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "> arrow
            keys</uicontrol> &lt; &gt; to go back and forward in time.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Press the Squares Icon to expand the view and show the bottles above each other.<fig id="fig_xg1_bsn_fcc" class="- topic/fig ">
            <image href="media/image3.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_yg1_bsn_fcc"
                   align="center"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Filter Icon</uicontrol> to filter the graph data. The screens below
